WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:15.410 --> 00:00:22.610
始まりも無いと　ぼやいて歩くだけ
This way home has no origin

00:00:22.610 --> 00:00:27.350
そんな帰り道
and I walk it feeling just morosely.

00:00:28.090 --> 00:00:32.150
君の声が聞こえ
When I heard your voice

00:00:32.150 --> 00:00:40.310
振り返られずに　胸を痛めてた
I didn’t need to turn around for my chest to hurt.

00:00:41.010 --> 00:00:44.190
誰もいない空　期待してたり…
I expect something from the forsaken sky...

00:00:44.190 --> 00:00:47.170
何も出来ないと諦めて 
But I give up since I can’t do anything

00:00:47.410 --> 00:00:50.670
同じ帰り道　そんな毎日
While I lament about the same way home

00:00:50.670 --> 00:00:53.910
ヤダよヤダよとか嘆いたら
And the same routine I’m sick of

00:00:55.430 --> 00:00:58.670
雫、無数の音
Droplets, the sound of innumerable of them.

00:00:58.670 --> 00:01:01.650
雨宿り、二人きり 
Together we take shelter from the rain

00:01:01.950 --> 00:01:08.050
目線も合わせずに　言葉を探してる
Searching for words without any eye contact

00:01:08.250 --> 00:01:14.410
やまないで夕立　永遠に隠してよ
Don’t stop, evening shower! Hide us forever.

00:01:14.650 --> 00:01:21.210
二人の隠れ処を　優しく包んでよ
Gently enwrap our hiding spot.

00:01:33.750 --> 00:01:37.750
そんなこともあって
Even if this happens

00:01:37.750 --> 00:01:46.310
また好きになって　そして近づけず…
I fall in love again without getting any closer…

00:01:46.570 --> 00:01:53.910
意識しすぎなんだ　でもきっかけとか　あれば…
I may be too cautious, but if there is a chance…

00:01:53.910 --> 00:01:58.710
苦労しない
I should not worry.

00:01:59.390 --> 00:02:02.670
誰もいない空　また君が来て
The sky is forsaken and you come again.

00:02:02.670 --> 00:02:05.510
待って！準備とかいるんです
Wait! I do have prepared

00:02:05.890 --> 00:02:09.050
だけどまたポツリ　空が怪しい
But it drizzles and the sky looks ominous.

00:02:09.050 --> 00:02:12.430
運命いたずら　困ります！
Fate tricked me - it will turn my plans upside down!

00:02:13.830 --> 00:02:16.990
雫、無数の音
Droplets, the sound of innumerable of them.

00:02:16.990 --> 00:02:19.970
雨宿り、二人きり
Together we take shelter from the rain.

00:02:20.250 --> 00:02:26.310
目線がたまに会い　言葉が紡がれる
Sometimes our gazes meet, connected by words.

00:02:26.550 --> 00:02:32.890
やまないで夕立 永遠に隠してよ
Don’t stop, evening shower! Hide us forever.

00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:39.370
二人の隠れ処を優しく包んでよ
Gently enwrap our hiding spot.

00:02:39.370 --> 00:02:42.370
照れた顔がいいの？
Is your embarrassed face any good?

00:02:42.650 --> 00:02:45.990
君はズルい人ね
You sure are cunning!

00:03:04.970 --> 00:03:08.290
二人だけの空　期待してたり
I expect something from our sky…

00:03:08.290 --> 00:03:11.430
途切れ途切れでも嬉しくて
It’s erratic but I’m happy

00:03:11.430 --> 00:03:14.630
同じ帰り道　そんな毎日
Because I always dreamed

00:03:14.630 --> 00:03:18.090
ずっとずっと夢見てたから
About the same way home and the same routine.

00:03:20.930 --> 00:03:25.830
雫、無限の恋　泣いてるよ、
Droplets, the sound of infinite love.

00:03:25.830 --> 00:03:27.190
雨の中
It’s crying in the rain

00:03:27.470 --> 00:03:33.770
二人の行方など　誰も知らないけど
Though no one knows about our whereabouts.

00:03:33.790 --> 00:03:40.290
やまないで夕立　永遠に隠してよ
Don’t stop, evening shower! Hide us forever.

00:03:40.290 --> 00:03:46.270
傘が二人の距離　縮めてくれるから
The umbrella is the reason the distance between us shortens after all.

00:03:46.470 --> 00:03:53.170
ちょっとだけ照れた顔　自信になってるよ
﻿Your slightly embarrassed face becomes my confidence.

